entry.title: Setup Pinterest Account
entry.content:
The following are steps to create a Pinterest Business account and how to setup the account.

Account Creation

  1. Go to https://www.pinterest.com/business/create.
  2. Go through the sign up process.
  3. ALWAYS select United States.

Account Setup

  1. Change your name and Pinterest URL. (If necessary)
  2. Start with 3 boards that represent your niche.
entry.summary: The following are steps to create a Pinterest Business account and how to setup the account.

entry.title: Save Pins
entry.content:
1. Check the Online Real Estate group page on Facebook for the latest pins to save.
  2. Save 1-3 pins from the group. (For each Pinterest account)
  3. Save pins from Pinterest for your own boards.

Remember

  1. Minimum 10 pins a day. (Total Per Account)
  2. Maximum 30 pins a day. (Total Per Account)
